\ testing read write speeds to SAMS memory

NEEDS @P  FROM DSK1.SAMS

HEX
    1000 CONSTANT 4K
    7FFF CONSTANT 32K
    FFFF CONSTANT 64K

: ERASE    0 FILL ;
: BLANKS  BL FILL ;

: 32KBYTES    32K 0 DO    I I C!P   LOOP ;
: 32KWORDS    32K 0 DO    I I !P   2+ LOOP ;

: ERASE32K    32K 0 DO   I PAGED 4K ERASE   4K +LOOP ;
: 32KBLANKS   32K 0 DO   I PAGED 4K BLANKS  4K +LOOP ;

: ERASE64K    64K 0 DO   I PAGED 4K ERASE   4K +LOOP ;
: 64KBLANKS   64K 0 DO   I PAGED 4K BLANKS  4K +LOOP ;

